Terry Martin, 48, shot his girlfriend Laurice Hampton after she asked for half of his winnings .
Hampton, who was critically injured from a gunshot wound, was able to call 911 about 6:30am Saturday to report the shootings before she died a few hours later .
The couple had known each other since childhood and had lived together for several years .
Martin was sentenced in July 2012 to a day in jail and fined $214 .